content.description: The northern routes on Reata Pass West are all located near the east prow. Little Yosemite is a right facing corner to roof system. 1 1/2" crack in slick corner leads to right roof exit. The best little route in Phoenix and the best 5.7 at the Pinnacle Peak in the day.
content.protection: small to medium nuts and friends
content.location: North side of wall. Route base is slightly shielded from view, but no other way in.....

content.description: Has both a sunny south side and shaded north side. Old routes done by unknown parties sit in an around this neat area. On top, there was the infamous 7' round boulder that drunken climbers tried to trundle for years to no avail.
